description:
Darkness Radio presents Supernatural News/ParaShare Roman Ghosts & Trips to Hell Edition

Dave & Tim share some laughs and memories from the past as well as a look at the weird world news of the supernatural this week.  Roman Centurian Ghost sightings, Megan Fox goes to Hell, Dave vs. Paranormal Real Estate, PLUS your emailed stories of supernatural shenanigans and a Brand New Theater of the Mind!
